    * bugfix project name

* v0.4.0.dev1 - 14.11.2017 - `compare v0.3.1...v0.4.0.dev1 <https://github.com/wearehoods/django-ya-model-publisher/compare/v0.3.1...v0.4.0.dev1>`_ 

